Stopwatch Web Application

An intuitive and responsive Stopwatch Web Application designed for precise time tracking and lap recording. Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, this project demonstrates essential front-end development skills.

Key Features

Start, Pause, and Reset functionality for complete timer control.

Lap Timer to record multiple laps with ease.

Real-time, accurate time display.

Fully responsive design, optimized for all devices.

About

Created as part of my learning journey and internship experience at Prodigy InfoTech, this project showcases my ability to build interactive and user-friendly web applications.
